rows.label: qev050503_MSG0001
rows.name: W-wait! Please, no! AAAAAAH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0002
rows.name:
Please do not shout, dearest human female.
I merely have a request of you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0003
rows.name: Someone help me! HEEEEEELP![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0004
rows.name:
I ask that you listen... Er, if it's not a bother...
LISTEN TO ME! *ahem* If you please, madam.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0005
rows.name: Heeelp! You there! This...thing is threatening me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0006
rows.name: I beg your pardon, madam! I am doing no such thing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0007
rows.name:
The hell you aren't! You just grabbed me by the lapels
and said I had to listen to what you said![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0008
rows.name: And what part of that is threatening, exactly?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0009
rows.name: What part ISN'T threatening?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0010
rows.name: Of all the contrary... You, madam, are unreasonable![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0011
rows.name: Are you SERIOUS right now?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0012
rows.name: Nrrrgh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0013
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0014
rows.name:
Bah. This is going absolutely nowhere.
...Hmm? Ho there! Good [ST:gender p1=sir p2=madam ]! Hold, please![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0015
rows.name:
Is that...? It IS! You're the BLADE who assisted me
before, are you not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0016
rows.name:
Ten thousand of the most sincerest apologies to foist
this on you so suddenly,  but could I ask you to
acquire for me a suitable sword?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0017
rows.name:
He wants a SWORD?! Don't give him a SWORD!
Are you freaking INSANE?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0018
rows.name: I feel it will make dealing with all of this much simpler.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0019
rows.name: EEEEEEEEEEEEEEK![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0020
rows.name:
Quickly now! A sword, if you please!
Before this gets any more out of hand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0021
rows.name:
I beg your pardon for my uncouth insistence,
but have you any word on that sword yet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0022
rows.name:
I do apologize for my impatience. You are very kind to
assist me. Just please make haste if at all possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050503_MSG0023
rows.name:
My conversation with the lady here grows more
awkward by the minute...[ST:wait ]
